column1: # action - Mandatory parameter. Possible values: 1- add, 2- update, 3- delete, 6- add or update.
# userId - mandatory parameter for all actions. Represents the id of the KalturaUser.
# screenName - optional parameter to set the user's screenName property value
# gender - optional, possible values: 0- male, 1- female
# roleIds - optional parameter, default value NULL. Passed as a comma-separated string of  role IDs that should be attributed to the new user.
